# PowerEdge R510 (gen 11, 2U dual-socket, up to 12 LFF drives).
#
# UNTESTED — extrapolated from R410 (probed). Gen 11 Dells (iDRAC6/iDRAC7
# era) all have BMC firmware that obeys PWM literally — values <20%
# risk fan stall. Same MIN_FAN=20 floor expected.
#
# If you've probed this BMC and it tolerates lower, drop MIN_FAN here.

: "${MIN_FAN:=20}"
